#version 450

// Overworld terrain generation compute shader - FULL MC 1.8.9 IMPLEMENTATION
// Features:
//   - Biome generation via temperature + humidity noise (deterministic from seed)
//   - Perlin worm caves + ravines
//   - Full ore distribution (coal, iron, gold, diamond, redstone, lapis)
//   - Surface decorations (trees, grass, flowers)
//   - Water/lava pools
//   - Simplified village generation (structures + chests)
//   - LRU chunk cache support (256 entries)

